Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.34,0:00:08.09,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You know about neurosis? Wow, Lain. You’re going to have to start counseling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.92,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I know the word, not its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:13.85,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What kind of image?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.85,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,The mind changes and becomes distorted?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.68,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Yes. You’ve got the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.16,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That’s awful. You won’t teach me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:24.86,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.62,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,I’m really telling you that you got the general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:36.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Neurosis is a state in which there is nothing wrong with a person physically, yet the person has irrational fears and perceives threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:39.17,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,This places a lot of stress on the person and makes her feel sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.17,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It’s only inside of their heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We used to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:51.66,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But after a lot of research, we think that an imbalance of the autonomic nerves in the brain is related to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:55.81,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,What I mean is, something is wrong in the body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:01:01.57,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,We used to categorize physical symptoms as psychosomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:08.06,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But we’ve been finding more and more that conditions we thought were only of the mind involve the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:10.26,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Psychosomatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, Lain, if you ask so many questions, your head is going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.85,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’ve heard about people who lose a lot of weight because of stress, or go bald?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:20.94,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,That’s psychosomatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.08,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Lain, you don’t, by any chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.42,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No, I don’t have that kind of problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:29.92,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, I’m relieved. That was hasty of me!
